name: Blood for the devil
description:
A lot of time has been spent on this artwork. Story: The queen of an ancient land is forced to sacrifice her family to maintain her rule. This frame is part of a dark and short story that I am the author of my own story. In the future, I will depict the main parts of this story. The hand of the queen is blood and that animal is in the legends of the devil. In the next frame, the queen's wife is seen in a battle against the demonic army.
